metadata.name: Ode to Mr. Toad キノピオ
metadata.description:
1/1 Artwork sculpted and fully animated by Zoe Winters. This collectible includes a sculpture for any digital gallery as well as AR model to enjoy.

Toad is a servant to princess peach, and he constantly fails to protect her as she is kidnapped every game. Super Mario games have been a huge influence in the creation of the characters I make, and toad is my favorite character in the game.
